Digest: The Act makes budget changes for certain state agencies. (Flesch Readability Score:
66.1).
Modifies an appropriation from the General Fund to the Emergency Board.
Modifies limitations on expenditures for certain biennial expenses for specified state agencies.
Appropriates moneys from the General Fund to specified state agencies for specified biennial
expenses.
Declares an emergency, effective on passage.
